    "This credential is from %@. Do you want to switch to %@?" : {
      "comment" : "A confirmation prompt that appears when a user tries to log in with a credential that belongs to a different school than the one they are currently logged into. The argument is the name of the school the credential belongs to, and the second argument is the name of the school the user is currently logged into.",
